Vdfparser

This module covers the most of the interfaces utilized by steam web api.
Create a steamwebapi object and simply use methods to fetch results. (For complete method documentation look at pod).

	use Steamwebapi;
	use Data::Dumper;
	
	my $object = Steamwebapi->new();
	my $result = $object->GetAppList();
	print Dumper $result;
	
INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make && make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find detail documentation for this module with the
perldoc command or try the man command also

    	perldoc Steamwebapi
    	man Steamwebapi

